OL,3,CKingspan slammed in Grenfell report
OL,5,FIrish building materials company
OL,6,FKingspan has come in for criticism in
OL,7,Fthe final report on the Grenfell Tower
OL,8,Ffire.
OL,10,FSeventy-two people - ranging in age
OL,11,Ffrom an unborn baby to an 84-year-old
OL,12,Fwoman - died in the fire at the west
OL,13,FLondon tower block in June 2017.
OL,15,FThe report published on Wednesday is
OL,16,Fthe second of a long-running inquiry.
OL,17,FIt found 'decades of failure'
OL,18,Fcontributed to the tragedy.
