OL,3,CKingspan slammed in Grenfell report
OL,5,FKingspan acknowledged what it said
OL,6,Fwere "wholly unacceptable historical
OL,7,Ffailings" in the industry, insisting
OL,8,Fthese were "in no way reflective of
OL,9,Fhow we conduct ourselves as a group,
OL,10,Fthen or now". The firm said it was
OL,11,Fcommitted to providing safe and
OL,12,Fsustainable building solutions.
OL,14,FKingspan is also the main sponsor of
OL,15,FUlster Rugby. That two decade long
OL,16,Frelationship is to end in June 2025.
OL,18,FThe company said its K15 insulation
OL,19,Fproduct made up 5% of the insulation
OL,20,Fin the tower block and was used
OL,21,Fwithout its knowledge.
