OL,3,CKingspan slammed in Grenfell report
OL,5,FBut the report found that Kingspan
OL,6,F"knowingly created a "false market in
OL,7,Finsulation" from 2005 onwards for use
OL,8,Fon buildings over 18metres tall.
OL,10,FIt claimed its K15 product had been
OL,11,Fpart of a system that had been
OL,12,Fsuccessfully tested under the BS 8414
OL,13,Fcladding fire safety test, meaning it
OL,14,Fcould be used in the wall of any
OL,15,Fbuilding of that height regardless of
OL,16,Fits design or other components.
