OL,3,CKingspan slammed in Grenfell report
OL,5,FThe inquiry branded this a "false
OL,6,Fclaim", adding: "As Kingspan knew, K15
OL,7,Fcould not honestly be sold as suitable
OL,8,Ffor use in the external walls of
OL,9,Fbuildings over 18metres in height
OL,10,Fgenerally, but that is what it had
OL,11,Fsucceeded in doing for many years."
OL,13,FITV News Correspondent John Ray breaks
OL,14,Fdown the key findings of the long-
OL,15,Fawaited report.
