OL,3,CKingspan slammed in Grenfell report
OL,5,FKingspan relied on the results of a
OL,6,Fsingle cladding fire safety test
OL,7,Fperformed in 2005, on a system whose
OL,8,Fcomponents were not representative of
OL,9,Fa typical external wall, the report
OL,10,Fsaid, and found that the firm
OL,11,Fcontinued to rely on that test despite
OL,12,Fchanging the composition of K15 in
OL,13,F2006.
OL,15,FFurther tests on systems incorporating
OL,16,FK15 in the following two years were
OL,17,F"disastrous", the report said, but
OL,18,FKingspan did not withdraw the product
OL,19,Ffrom the market, "despite its own
OL,20,Fconcerns about its fire performance".
