OL,3,CKingspan slammed in Grenfell report
OL,5,FIn 2009, Kingspan obtained a
OL,6,Fcertificate that "contained false
OL,7,Fstatements about K15", the report
OL,8,Fsaid, and on which it relied "for many
OL,9,Fyears to sell the product", adding
OL,10,Fthat it made a "calculated decision"
OL,11,Fto use the certificate to "mask, or
OL,12,Fdistract from, the absence of
OL,13,Fsupporting test evidence".
