OL,3,CKingspan slammed in Grenfell report
OL,5,FThe report said Kingspan "cynically
OL,6,Fexploited" the industry's lack of
OL,7,Fdetailed knowledge about insulation
OL,8,Fand cladding fire safety tests, and
OL,9,F"relied on the fact that an
OL,10,Funsuspecting market was very likely to
OL,11,Frely on its own claim about the
OL,12,Fproduct".
OL,14,FResponding to the report, Kingspan
OL,15,Fsaid it had "long acknowledged the
OL,16,Fwholly unacceptable historical
OL,17,Ffailings that occurred in part of our
OL,18,FUK insulation business" but said these
OL,19,Fwere "in no way reflective of how we
OL,20,Fconduct ourselves as a group, then or
OL,21,Fnow".
